query:
SET @riv_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%Riverside%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- OB/GYN protocols (4800 series)
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@riv_id, '4801', 'Childbirth/Delivery', 'Obstetrical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Childbirth and Delivery. Normal delivery, cord clamping, and newborn care.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4802', 'Obstetrical Emergencies', 'Obstetrical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Obstetrical Emergencies. Cord prolapse, breech, and hemorrhage management.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4803', 'Eclampsia/Preeclampsia', 'Obstetrical', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Eclampsia and Preeclampsia. Magnesium sulfate and seizure management.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),

-- Pediatric protocols (4900 series)
(@riv_id, '4901', 'Pediatric Assessment', 'Pediatric', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Assessment. Age-appropriate assessment techniques.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4902', 'Pediatric Cardiac Arrest', 'Pediatric', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Cardiac Arrest. Age-appropriate CPR and medication dosing.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4903', 'Pediatric Respiratory Emergencies', 'Pediatric', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Respiratory Emergencies. Croup, asthma, and foreign body airway obstruction.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4904', 'Pediatric Seizures', 'Pediatric', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Seizures. Weight-based benzodiazepine dosing.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4905', 'Pediatric Trauma', 'Pediatric', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Trauma. Age-appropriate assessment and treatment.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4906', 'Neonatal Resuscitation', 'Pediatric', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Neonatal Resuscitation. NRP guidelines and newborn care.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
(@riv_id, '4907', 'Pediatric Diabetic Emergencies', 'Pediatric', 'Riverside County REMSA Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Diabetic Emergencies. Age-appropriate dextrose dosing.', 'https://rivcoready.org/remsa/policy-manual', '2022-10-04', 2022, NOW()),
